snippet.title: Captain Cosmo for the Atari 8-bit family
snippet.description:
Came also out for:

MSX 


Game description:

Prisoners preak loose and you have to shoot them and capture them to bring them back to the zoo

What I think:

Not a bad game, but it has "absolutely repetitive" written all over it...
